      <b data-is-speakable>Christopher Anderson, Catherine Croft Testify In Impeachment Inquiry</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Christopher Anderson, onetime aide to the former special envoy to Ukraine, will be interviewed along with Catherine Croft, who served as special adviser for Ukraine in the State Department.</b>
